    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pieces of textiles of any length, distinguished by having a width that is the full measure of the weft, which are the threads extending across the width of the loom.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
